在'''[[南海仲裁案|南海仲裁案]]'''中，各国政府和一些国际组织对其或多或少地表达了看法，这涉及[[南中国海领土争端|南中国海领土争端]]。这些国家和组织并不一定完全偏向某方，因为这关乎受争议地区的[[主权|主权]]问题。

== 南海岛礁主权及海洋权益的声索方 ==
=== 中华民国 ===
[[中华民国|中华民国]]并没有被邀请参加仲裁案，台湾的大多数媒体对其评价甚低<ref>{{cite web |url=https://seasresearch.wordpress.com/2016/04/13/water-source-crucial-in-determining-status-of-itu-aba/ |title=Water source crucial in determining status of Itu Aba |first= |last=hueviet |date=13 April 2016 |publisher= |access-date=2016-07-12 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126024709/https://seasresearch.wordpress.com/2016/04/13/water-source-crucial-in-determining-status-of-itu-aba/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。菲律宾方面认为，台方控制的[[太平岛|太平岛]]不是岛屿而是礁石<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mb.com.ph/ph-leaves-taiping-island-issue-to-un/|title=PH leaves ‘Taiping Island’ issue to UN|first=The Manila|last=Bulletin|publisher=}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。对此，中华民国前总统[[马英九|马英九]]对此予以反驳，认为菲律宾的看法完全错误<ref>{{cite web|url = http://focustaiwan.tw/news/aipl/201605170030.aspx|title = Taiping Island deserves exclusive economic zone: president - Politics - FOCUS TAIWAN - CNA ENGLISH NEWS|publisher = |access-date = 2016-07-12|archive-date = 2019-12-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191210143110/http://focustaiwan.tw/news/aipl/201605170030.aspx|dead-url = no}}</ref>。中华民国政府邀请仲裁庭5个仲裁员和菲律宾方面到太平岛鉴识。菲律宾拒绝了邀请<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.chinapost.com.tw/taiwan/intl-community/2016/05/14/466118/Philippines-rejects.htm |title = Philippines rejects invitation to Taiping: Foreign Ministry |publisher =  |access-date = 2016-07-12 |archive-date = 2017-08-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170830145125/http://www.chinapost.com.tw/taiwan/intl-community/2016/05/14/466118/philippines-rejects.htm |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

===越南===
2014年12月11日，[[越南政府|越南政府]]表达了看法，宣示对该案的支持。[[越南|越南]]当局提出三点：支持菲律宾的诉求；拒绝承认中国方面单方面提出的“[[九段线|九段线]]”要求；要求仲裁庭也关注[[帕拉塞尔群岛|帕拉塞尔群岛]]（中国称其为西沙群岛）的主权问题<ref name="vietnam">{{cite news |url = http://mobile.bloomberg.com/news/2014-12-12/south-china-sea-tensions-flare-as-vietnam-files-stance-to-court.html |work = Bloomberg |title = Bloomberg Business |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141213103712/http://mobile.bloomberg.com/news/2014-12-12/south-china-sea-tensions-flare-as-vietnam-files-stance-to-court.html |archivedate = 2014-12-13 |accessdate = 2016-07-12 }}</ref>。

===其它===
[[文莱|文莱]]也对该案表达了关切，并也对南中国海问题提交过自己的主张<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.un.org/depts/los/clcs_new/submissions_files/preliminary/brn2009preliminaryinformation.pdf|title = Brunei Darussalam's Preliminary Submission concerning the Outer Limits of its Continental Shelf|accessdate = November 19, 2013|publisher = [[United_Nations|United Nations]]|archive-date = 2020-11-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201128153039/https://www.un.org/depts/los/clcs_new/submissions_files/preliminary/brn2009preliminaryinformation.pdf|dead-url = no}}</ref>。2009年5月，[[马来西亚|马来西亚]]、越南，在[[国际海洋法法庭|国际海洋法法庭]]提出关于岛屿主权归属的诉讼，声称其拥有其相关的[[大陆架|大陆架]]和[[专属经济区|专属经济区]]。中华人民共和国拒绝接受，声称其违反“九段线”，主張應該完全依據《[[南海各方行為宣言|南海各方行為宣言]]》。菲律宾质疑马来西亚的主张，指出其与[[北婆罗洲|北婆罗洲]]{{Link-en|北婆罗洲领土争端|North Borneo dispute|产生}}重叠<ref name= "Malaysia Vietnam" /><ref>[http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/ce/cemy/eng/xw/t579238.htm Wen Jiabao Holds Talks with Malaysian Prime Minister Najib] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/ce/cemy/eng/xw/t579238.htm |date=20190624032609 }}. [[中华人民共和国外交部|中华人民共和国外交部]]</ref>。

[[印尼|印尼]]认为中国声索主权的“岛屿”大部分为[[礁石|礁石]]，不能长时间露在水面上，所以认为中国的主张是完全没有根据的<ref name= "Malaysia Vietnam" >{{cite web |url=http://www.un.org/Depts/los/clcs_new/submissions_files/submission_mysvnm_33_2009.htm |title=Submissions to the Commission: Joint submission by Malaysia and the Socialist Republic of Viet Nam |date=May 3, 2011 |accessdate=November 19, 2013 |publisher=[[United_Nations|United Nations]] Division for Ocean Affairs and the Law of the Sea |archive-date=2021-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213043526/https://www.un.org/Depts/los/clcs_new/submissions_files/submission_mysvnm_33_2009.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name = "Davenport">{{cite web |url=http://southchinaseastudies.org/en/conferences-and-seminars-/second-international-workshop/608-clcs-submissions-and-claims-in-the-south-china-sea-by-robert-c-beckman-a-tara-davenport |title=CLCS submissions and claims in the South China Sea, by Robert C. Beckman & Tara Davenport |date=August 11, 2011 |accessdate=November 19, 2013 |publisher=SouthChinaSeaStudies.org |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306082720/http://southchinaseastudies.org/en/conferences-and-seminars-/second-international-workshop/608-clcs-submissions-and-claims-in-the-south-china-sea-by-robert-c-beckman-a-tara-davenport |archive-date=2016-03-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

