==区域集团==
[[非洲联盟|非洲联盟]]的一位副主席支持中国的立场。<ref name="fmprc.gov.cn"/>[[阿拉伯国家联盟|阿拉伯国家联盟]]秘书长[[纳比勒·阿拉比|纳比勒·阿拉比]]说，阿拉伯国家支持中国维护国家主权和领土完整的立场。然而，阿拉伯国家联盟还强调，主权国家的解决方法和联合国海洋法公约的签署国一样，应得到尊重。<ref>{{cite news|title=Arab States Extend Support to China on Its South China Sea Policy  Read more:|url=http://sputniknews.com/asia/20160513/1039583944/arab-states-china.html|accessdate=23 May 2016|work=Sputnik News|date=13 May 2016|archive-date=2016-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160522220305/http://sputniknews.com/asia/20160513/1039583944/arab-states-china.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[欧洲联盟|欧洲联盟]]鼓励争端的各方能通过对话和合作寻求和平解决，并要依照国际法，尤其是涉及到联合国公约海洋法时<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rappler.com/nation/69293-philippines-aquino-eu-barroso-unclos|title=Philippines, EU show common stance on China|publisher=|accessdate=2016-07-12|archive-date=2017-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170111032146/http://www.rappler.com/nation/69293-philippines-aquino-eu-barroso-unclos|dead-url=no}}</ref>。欧盟外事发表声明称“欧盟期盼的是一个在国际法的原则下——特别是在联合国海洋法公约原则下的建立海洋秩序”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-southchinasea-usa-eu-idUSKCN0SO22G20151031|title=European Union sides with United States on South China Sea incident|date=2015-10-31|publisher=|via=Reuters|accessdate=2016-07-12|archive-date=2016-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624201048/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-southchinasea-usa-eu-idUSKCN0SO22G20151031|dead-url=no}}</ref>。欧盟还强调“中国应当尊重裁决结果”<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/apr/19/south-china-sea-britain-court-arbitration-ruling-binding |title = South China Sea: Britain says court of arbitration ruling must be binding |first =  |last = Reuters |date = 2016-04-19 |publisher =  |access-date = 2016-07-12 |archive-date = 2020-12-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201223182510/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/apr/19/south-china-sea-britain-court-arbitration-ruling-binding |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

[[捷克|捷克]]陆军将军切赫·帕维尔说，[[北约|北约]]尊崇“以规则为基础的国际体系”，并以此来解决国际争端。他补充说，“中国是一个签署了《海洋法公约》的国家，中国应该尊重规则。”<ref name= "Czech" />，北约支持双方进行以政治和外交为基础的谈判，用“以规则为基础的国际体系”以及“和平的方式”解决“不和谐”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/east-asia/nato-has-no-legal-platforms-to-intervene-militarily-in-south-china-sea|title=Nato has 'no legal platforms' to intervene militarily in South China Sea|accessdate=2016-07-13|archive-date=2016-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160607071851/http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/east-asia/nato-has-no-legal-platforms-to-intervene-militarily-in-south-china-sea|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[上海合作组织|上海合作组织]]秘书长拉希德·奥利莫夫明确声明“所有上海合作组织成员国支持中国为维护南海的和平与稳定进行努力。”该声明称与之有直接关系的国家应通过谈判和协商解决符合所有双边条约，在中国南海（DOC）各方行为宣言谈判协商解决。声明还敦促所有人尊重“主权国家自行解决纠纷的方式”的权利，坚决反对外界介入到中国南海问题以及对争端国际化的尝试。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.china.org.cn/world/2016-05/25/content_38530226.htm|title=SCO supports peace and stability in South China Sea|author=李珅|publisher=|accessdate=2016-07-12|archive-date=2016-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160526101542/http://www.china.org.cn/world/2016-05/25/content_38530226.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==学者分析==
===中国声称的“九段线”===
*中国南海研究院高级研究员吴士存认为，中国对九段线内的领土主权声明早于海洋法公约半个世纪，根据国际法不溯过往的基本原则来看，现有国际法不能规定过去的事实存在<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.cntv.cn/2014/08/22/VIDE1408651799056547.shtml|title=Chinese scholar: China holds more solid claim - CCTV News - CCTV.com English|first=Zhang|last=Jingya|publisher=|accessdate=29 June 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811223435/http://english.cntv.cn/2014/08/22/VIDE1408651799056547.shtml|archive-date=2016-08-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
*[[维多利亚大学|维多利亚大学]]法学部教授特德·麦克多曼认为，历史性水域不受海洋法公约规管。[[国际法院|国际法院]]在1982年对[[突尼斯|突尼斯]]和[[利比亚|利比亚]]领海争议的判决中显示，「歷史性權利」由[[國際習慣法|國際習慣法]]规定，海洋法公约没有约束性<ref name="JayakumarKoh2014">{{cite book|author1=S. Jayakumar|author2=Tommy Koh|author3=Robert Beckman|title=The South China Sea Disputes and Law of the Sea|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=MR5CBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA152|date=29 August 2014|publisher=Edward Elgar Publishing|isbn=978-1-78347-727-2|pages=152–153}}</ref>。
*国家安全法中心和海洋法与政策中心主任约翰·诺顿·摩尔说，中国的“九段线”声明是非法的，在现有海洋法中明禁此举。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.law.virginia.edu/html/news/2016_spr/moore.htm|title=UVA Law Professor John Norton Moore Explains South China Sea Controversy|publisher=|accessdate=29 June 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160923145123/http://www.law.virginia.edu/html/news/2016_spr/moore.htm|archive-date=2016-09-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>他还认为，九段线实际上不利于中国的整体利益。他说：“如果全世界各国都效仿中国设立九段线这种做法宣称领土主权，那么这将损害中国在世界各地的利益。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://amti.csis.org/a-case-of-rocks-islands/|title=A CASE OF ROCKS OR ISLANDS? Examining the South China Sea Arbitration|publisher=Asia Maratime Transparency Initiative|access-date=2016-07-12|archive-date=2021-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223171518/https://amti.csis.org/a-case-of-rocks-islands/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===菲律宾的声索===
*[[中央兰开夏大学|中央兰开夏大学]]哈里斯国际法终身讲席教授邹克渊在他出版的新书中称，中国在南沙群岛（斯普拉特利群岛）的专属经济区权利被菲律宾刻意忽略，而控制方实际控制的陆地拥有其周围的海事管辖权。案件对专属经济区的判决含有水分，菲律宾以此获得其“微弱”的国际支援。<ref name="Zou2005">{{cite book|author=Keyuan Zou|title=Law of the Sea in East Asia: Issues And Prospects|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=34_T4TRmELQC|date=January 2005|publisher=Psychology Press|isbn=978-0-415-35074-7|access-date=2016-07-12|archive-date=2017-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170724085542/https://books.google.com/books?id=34_T4TRmELQC|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*[[国立臺灣師範大學|国立臺灣師範大學]]政治學研究所教授王冠雄认为，菲律宾的申诉书本身“可疑”。菲律宾在破坏该地区的稳定局势。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://thediplomat.com/2016/01/the-philippines-dubious-claims-in-south-china-sea-arbitration/|title=The Philippines’ Dubious Claims in South China Sea Arbitration|publisher=The Diplomat|author=Kuan-Hsiung Wang|date=January 26, 2016|access-date=2016-07-12|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029013832/https://thediplomat.com/2016/01/the-philippines-dubious-claims-in-south-china-sea-arbitration/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===判决结果===
*[[国际法院|国际法院]]前法官{{Link-en|阿卜杜勒·科罗马|Abdul Koroma}}指出，中国拒绝仲裁是正确的<ref name="eastday.com">{{Cite web|url=http://english.eastday.com/auto/n917358/u1ai8550761.html|title=South China Sea tribunal has no legal validity-Eastday|accessdate=2016-08-24|work=english.eastday.com|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630152453/http://english.eastday.com/auto/n917358/u1ai8550761.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*{{link-en|德拉萨大学|De La Salle University}}政治学助理教授，过去是菲律宾众议院政策顾问（2009- 2015年）的理查德·贾瓦德·海达里安说，中国的最终目的是获得对邻近海域的实际控制权。唯一的问题是：它能否以及如何实现这一目标。并且他认为，国际仲裁庭没有实际力量让中国接受仲裁结果<ref>{{cite web|url=http://amti.csis.org/the-battle-of-the-hague-philippines-v-china-in-the-south-china-sea/|title=THE BATTLE OF THE HAGUE: PHILIPPINES V. CHINA IN THE SOUTH CHINA SEA|publisher=Asia Maratime Transparency Initiative|access-date=2016-07-12|archive-date=2020-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223190202/https://amti.csis.org/the-battle-of-the-hague-philippines-v-china-in-the-south-china-sea/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

